      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, u ever think about how much info actually goes through these big data entry firms? i've been looking at the patterns in the logistics logs i process and it's... way more than just shipping stuff. it feels like there's a much bigger picture being built here, like a massive shift coming. does it ever feel like the people at the top are keeping the real purpose of all this data from the people actually doing the work?",
